      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"difficult transition\" for coal sounds kind of vague though. Like, what does that actually mean for the towns that rely on it? Is there really a balanced way to look at this if the coal plants are being phased out, or is the shift to solar just a given at this point?",
